==Serbian==
===Etymology===
From Turkish [[bre#Turkish|bre]].
===Cyrillic spelling===
*[[бре#Serbian|бре]]
===Intensifier===
'''bre'''
# used to express passion about the point of a sentence, at any part of a sentence
# similar to English [[fuck]] or [[hell]], but not vulgar, e.g.:
#:''Šta si '''bre''' to uradio!?'' (What the '''[[fuck#Intensifier|fuck]]''' did you do!?)
===Interjection===
'''bre'''
#[[hey]]
#[[yo]] (''slang'')
